<emphasis id="F48B66D12D9D2A46316142177DE0ABF8" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">BRAZIL.</emphasis>
Sine loc., 
<emphasis id="592607C87ED96D5B5232639DB58BFF93" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">W.J. Burchell</emphasis>
858A (K). 
<emphasis id="69992607606C7D86C3D58C61E6577FE0" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Mato Grosso</emphasis>
: Novo Mundo, P. Est. do Cristalino, 
<emphasis id="109B033EC690ABE0FC7ABDEDE0F7B779" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">G. Henicka et al.</emphasis>
25 (K); Alta Floresta, P. Est. do Cristolino, 
<emphasis id="F510E53B004825E18F720F68FAB0AAD8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D. Sasaki et al.</emphasis>
1355 (K); Santa Cruz do Xingu, 
<emphasis id="4E88DF1FE42BABEBB0D0A4F32B74DEC4" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D.C. Zappi et al.</emphasis>
3062 (K, RB). 
<emphasis id="8C1D6886DAEB6DFE834EF2DDFBF24378" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Tocantins</emphasis>
: Mun. Pres. Kennedy, Faz. Primavera, 
<emphasis id="2F56140C7A6B43C9C2CB123D28001ADB" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">T. Plowman et al.</emphasis>
8128 (FTG, MG); P.N. do Araguaia, Ilha da Bananal, 
<emphasis id="07FDC0D04148298A9CDD5AB24AFCA855" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
R.C. 
<normalizedToken id="C71CB11AE92AB6B486A3597790C57DEF" originalValue="Mendonça">Mendonca</normalizedToken>
et al.
</emphasis>
3951 (IBGE, OXF, US). 
<emphasis id="F109B4CC481DE76870516B4644F1F90F" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<normalizedToken id="FE8554896B65B317D5A56CC6A16D21F7" originalValue="Pará">Para</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
: Araguaia, 20 km W of 
<normalizedToken id="77E692507302251A169227E666881CF0" originalValue="Redenção">Redencao</normalizedToken>
